OL,3,CAutism and ADHD waiting lists in Wales
OL,4,C'could triple in two years'
OL,6,FThe number of children waiting for an
OL,7,Fautism or ADHD assessment in Wales
OL,8,Fcould nearly triple to 61,000 over the
OL,9,Fnext two years, a committee has heard.
OL,11,FSarah Murphy, Wales' mental health
OL,12,Fminister, told the Senedd's children's
OL,13,Fcommittee that 20,770 children were
OL,14,Fwaiting for a neurodevelopmental
OL,15,Fassessment in September last year.
OL,17,F"The assessment we've got from the NHS
OL,18,FExecutive is that we're going to see,
OL,19,Fby March 2027, between 41,000 to
OL,20,F61,000 people waiting for these
OL,21,Fassessments," she said.
