OL,3,CAutism and ADHD waiting lists in Wales
OL,4,C'could triple in two years'
OL,6,FBy comparison, according to freedom of
OL,7,Finformation (FoI) requests, around
OL,8,F4,100 children were awaiting an ADHD
OL,9,For autism assessment in September 2021.
OL,11,FSpeaking to ITV Wales, Wendy Thomas,
OL,12,FHead of the National Neurodivergence
OL,13,FNervice in Wales, said: "There isn't
OL,14,Fjust one solution to it. There's got
OL,15,Fto be a number of solutions.
