OL,3,CAutism and ADHD waiting lists in Wales
OL,4,C'could triple in two years'
OL,6,F"What we all want is that we don't
OL,7,Fhave children waiting for a very long
OL,8,Ftime on waiting lists. But, what we
OL,9,Fdon't want to do either, is not have
OL,10,Fchildren accessing the support that
OL,11,Fthey need if they do need it."
OL,13,FHazel Lim, a mother from Swansea who
OL,14,Fhas been diagnosed with autism, said
OL,15,Fshe had to battle to get a diagnosis
OL,16,Ffor her son.
