OL,6,F"I remember a few times I was crying
OL,7,Fso badly in the meetings. I didn't
OL,8,Ffeel like I was being understood. If
OL,9,Fthere wasn't anything, why would I
OL,10,Fbring this to the school to discuss?"
OL,11,Fshe said of getting a diagnosis for
OL,12,Fher son.
OL,14,FGiving evidence on Thursday (9
OL,15,FJanuary), Ms Murphy, who is
OL,16,Fresponsible for neurodevelopmental
OL,17,Fconditions, learning disability, and
OL,18,Fdementia, pointed to a "one-off
OL,19,Ffunding" of #3m for health boards.
