OL,4,C'could triple in two years'
OL,6,F"That assessment means a lot to
OL,7,Fchildren, young people and their
OL,8,Ffamilies," she said. "I was speaking
OL,9,Fto the National Autistic Society
OL,10,Fyesterday and they said 'we've raised
OL,11,Fso much awareness but now we need to
OL,12,Fride that wave towards understanding
OL,13,Fand acceptance'."
OL,15,FShe said health boards are bringing in
OL,16,Fadditional capacity from the private
OL,17,Fsector in an effort to meet demand but
OL,18,Fcautioned that this is unsustainable.
