OL,3,CAutism and ADHD waiting lists in Wales
OL,4,C'could triple in two years'
OL,6,FAlbert Heaney, the chief social care
OL,7,Fofficer for Wales, said health boards
OL,8,Fare confident an extra 2,000
OL,9,Fassessments will be delivered by the
OL,10,Fend of March.
OL,12,FHe said: "Importantly, the money is on
OL,13,Fcondition that they are delivered.
OL,14,FIt's coming the other way around on
OL,15,Fthis occasion ... it's not money
OL,16,Fthat's given out, the money is on
OL,17,Fdelivery."
